{"tid":1360450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：白衣人鐵通狂毆兼借機捏胸","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:08:37.000Z","uid":166993,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac8581c3dfdef536a5ae55b159f03438c9b805e","tid":1360450,"uid":166993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"元朗周日發生無差別襲擊事件，暴徒除了襲擊無辜市民，還<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藉機向少女摸胸</span></span>。受害人Janice（化名）向《蘋果》表示，無法想像自己當晚會被非禮及打至骨折，至今都不敢報警，恐怕反被警方誣告。<br />\n<br />\n不願上鏡的Janice今年20多歲，事發2日後才冷靜下來接受《蘋果》訪問。她解釋，當晚本來在家看電視，突然收到訊息得知元朗發生襲擊，當時有朋友身在附近無法逃脫，於是她與另一名友人決定駕車前往營救。二人駛到元朗西鐵站附近時，驚見前方有白衣人狂毆市民，Janice立即下車喝止，「當時好嬲，都冇諗過會俾人打，仲以為可以喝停佢哋」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，白衣惡漢隨即改為襲擊Janice及其友人，把他們按在地上，以鐵通等武器不斷毆打，期間Janice感到有惡漢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">故意伸手大力捏其胸部</span></span>，最後因為暴徒改為襲擊其他目標，Janice和友人才可趁機逃走，再駕車前往醫院治理，診治發現她腳部骨折，腳趾亦受傷流血需要縫針處理。至於本身想營救的朋友，則成功坐車離開。<br />\n<br />\n現時Janice需要撐拐杖行路，未知腳部會否出現永久損害。她表示，至今無法想像自己會經歷這些事情，「我真係冇諗過會俾人打到骨折同非禮，我成世人都冇骨折過」。她說自己過往曾經參與示威，因此不敢報警，深怕會反被警方濫控暴動罪，何況自己認不到暴徒的樣貌，也不知如何提供資料。她又指，大量影片都清晰拍到暴徒的樣貌，「警察有心要拉人點會拉唔到呀？根本唔想拉啫嘛，大家夾埋嘅！」<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190724&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59858789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190724%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59858789&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9fQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d15eef21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190724%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59858789&h=e40254e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190724&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59858789</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727 元朗見</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b74073842d16041a9d347e5f3fbb3fb673a9df9","tid":1360450,"uid":77740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"睇到嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc19d6d5e7e05ef3a54803d58cca57cd769ff4a","tid":1360450,"uid":195412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"push, 就算捉唔到d撚樣，呢d惡行都係我地遊行既動力"},{"pid":"549070a9c5d9a03bd7e5d24c8bfcd02d95893892","tid":1360450,"uid":208813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9792f0b04836331de8ab2ad575e93f9aede880d7","tid":1360450,"uid":195258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c6cdca9c893e2a20e3b4b2cbaa4ec21276b17d","tid":1360450,"uid":224323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"畜牲，727遇左要見紅，有幾紅得幾紅，紅嗰個係你。"},{"pid":"3cb67034d451fc20e92e7410f1c5a3b5b566f31f","tid":1360450,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"a1898b2b58f19ae2d3ec25235de04faa6481654e","tid":1360450,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8644b7d38dc6831e36fc8d43ab4fd5c82cb82c","tid":1360450,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思!!<br />\n後日0726就係機場集會!!!<br />\n機場有無數外國旅客!!!<br />\n係對外發出香港嘅SOS求救訊號嘅大好機會!!!<br />\n一定要搞大佢!!!<br />\n宜家一齊推&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n❲0726機場❳ 多國語言 發動全球文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[繼續開花] 到我地機師做野喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359574</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1f02e010bf9219371f7c105822eb31141d77352","tid":1360450,"uid":212